      <p align="center">&nbsp;</p>



      <p align="center"><b><font face="Courier New, Courier, mono" size="5">From<i>



        Blues</i> to Haikus: An interview with Charles Henri Ford</font></b></p>



      <div align="center"><font face="Courier New, Courier, mono" size="3"><b>by 



        Rhonda Roland Shearer and Thomas Girst</b></font></div>



      </td>



  </tr>



  <tr>



    <td height="189">



      <p>&nbsp;</p>



      <font face="Courier New, Courier, mono" size="2"> </font>



      <table width="260" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left">



