      <font face="Courier New, Courier, mono" size="2">



      <P><I><B>R.S.</b></i> And so he apparently worked very hard on this issue,



        the Duchamp issue, it says. What this talks about is that he heard that



        Duchamp went through a lot of trouble to make this special effect for



        the cover and apparently there’s all sorts of levels of trick photography



        in making this cover. Do you recall?</P>



      <B></B>



      <P><I><B>C.H.F.</b></i> No.</P>



      <B></B>



      <P><I><B>R.S.</b></i> But it’s beautiful.</P>



      <B></B>



      <P><I><B>C.H.F.</b></i> Yes it is.</P>



      <B></B> </font>



