              cover for André Breton's <i>Young Cherry Trees Secured Against Hares</i>,



              New York, 1946,<br>



              © 2000 Succession Marcel Duchamp, ARS/N.Y., ADAGP/Paris</b></font></div>



          </td>



        </tr>



